Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.40,0:00:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天氣好好\N今天一定會曬得很黑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.90,0:00:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天一定要搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.14,0:00:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,珠代…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.78,0:00:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,珠代，妳不是說\N要幫我一起做便當的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.26,0:00:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種天氣去海邊玩\N再好不過了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.44,0:00:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個也沒來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.71,0:00:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.78,0:00:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該把集合時間\N約的晚一點的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.61,0:00:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都要接受懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.16,0:01:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遙遠夜空閃耀的小星星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.63,0:01:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想必還無人發現
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.44,0:01:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但它毫不氣餒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.14,0:01:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,依然如此閃爍光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.61,0:01:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎跟我有點相像
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.75,0:01:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在擠滿人群的街頭徘徊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.32,0:01:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎已不明白什麼才是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.10,0:01:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,努力尋找自我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.73,0:01:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要敞開胸懷去接收
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.60,0:01:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定會明白心靈的悸動\NI wanna get it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.44,0:01:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夢想就在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.31,0:02:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不論何時  就在你身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.12,0:02:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此渺小
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.05,0:02:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少是一個開始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.66,0:02:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相信遲早會發現
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.63,0:02:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這世上獨一無二的我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.53,0:02:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要堅定信心就好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.57,0:02:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前途在望  做我唯一的天使
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.24,0:02:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏天的海邊\N某人正在暗戀著某人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.96,0:02:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小咲咲\N有什麼需要我幫忙的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.53,0:02:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那妳來幫我打蛋好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.50,0:02:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.91,0:02:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看我也來學做菜好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.14,0:02:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正我天生就不是這塊料
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.85,0:02:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美咲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.65,0:02:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要上班了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.05,0:02:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祥子，妳早
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.65,0:02:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早，珠代
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.55,0:02:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真好，還可以去海邊玩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.06,0:03:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪像我得工作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.59,0:03:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連吃早餐的時間都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.16,0:03:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.03,0:03:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祥子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.16,0:03:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來，妳的便當
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.73,0:03:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.13,0:03:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.70,0:03:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祝妳們幾個今天玩得愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.32,0:03:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們來囉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.36,0:03:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼慢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.53,0:03:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起\N是我準備便當拖太久了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.03,0:03:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實也沒等多久
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.97,0:03:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這什麼態度啊你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.07,0:03:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鳩子，妳的感冒已經好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.57,0:03:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了，我們快點走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.77,0:03:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不然搭不上電車了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.08,0:03:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.74,0:03:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乾脆我們兩個自己去海邊玩\N怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.48,0:03:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託，妳就饒了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.18,0:03:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真的就這麼討厭跟我在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.83,0:03:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位\N每個人零食只買了三百塊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.46,0:04:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼不早點說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.90,0:04:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害得我買了一大堆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.67,0:04:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要罰你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.80,0:04:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你自己才應該接受懲罰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.94,0:04:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼晚才來集合還敢說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.61,0:04:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路上搞不好會塞車
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.41,0:04:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫我們提早集合\N根本就沒意義嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.12,0:04:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尾形，你幹嘛認真嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.52,0:04:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰說零食只能買三百塊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.42,0:04:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又不是小學生了嘛，對不對
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.16,0:04:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不管，你要接受懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.63,0:04:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳沒睡好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.90,0:04:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該不會又熬夜練習到早上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.17,0:04:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是因為忙著做便當
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.17,0:04:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真希望能夠趕快嚐嚐看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.57,0:04:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你該追的是她的女兒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.12,0:04:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到海了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.59,0:04:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不幫我拿一點，惡魔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.69,0:05:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起\N東西統統都讓你一個人拿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.29,0:05:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.23,0:05:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也幫你拿一點好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.47,0:05:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…這…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.07,0:05:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…那件泳裝還滿好看的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.78,0:05:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.94,0:05:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小光，說妳的泳裝很好看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.35,0:05:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，不是她的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.12,0:05:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美咲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.92,0:05:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快過來…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.12,0:05:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.23,0:05:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都沒有人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.47,0:05:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總算有一點放暑假的感覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.30,0:05:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也這麼覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.81,0:05:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們兩個一直在忙著\N參加天使領域的比賽嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.55,0:05:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這陽傘好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.68,0:05:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.58,0:05:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虎太郎，謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.05,0:05:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰理妳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.99,0:06:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來游泳吧，很涼快
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.30,0:06:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛，真倒楣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.30,0:06:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尾形，這個放這兒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.37,0:06:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，就放那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.24,0:06:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為會有很多人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.51,0:06:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為今天不是假日嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.44,0:06:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子\N海邊小店好像還有在營業
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.28,0:06:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尾形，你知不知道老大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.88,0:06:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正在忙著接受懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.05,0:06:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥變成一條魚了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.82,0:06:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫我去哪裡找海鮮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.82,0:06:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既沒有魷魚也沒有章魚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.22,0:06:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滾開…小心我吃了你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.60,0:06:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,西瓜應該被海水冰透了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.00,0:06:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看我拿手的旋轉魔球
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.44,0:06:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虎太郎，幫我擦防曬油
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.08,0:06:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳少作夢了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.34,0:06:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是隨便說說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.55,0:07:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想玩就一起過去玩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.18,0:07:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實你明明很想玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.42,0:07:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳少煩啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.52,0:07:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好渴，你們想喝什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.66,0:07:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看，我去買點刨冰回來好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.59,0:07:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係，我去買就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.36,0:07:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.37,0:07:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,命中目標
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.74,0:07:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最拿手的熱血殺球
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.97,0:07:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,珠代，妳幹嘛對著我打
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.74,0:07:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看還是我去買刨冰好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.48,0:07:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要草莓冰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.44,0:07:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要哈密瓜冰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.75,0:07:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.05,0:07:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虎太郎要檸檬冰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.42,0:07:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這兒不會熱嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.19,0:07:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海風吹起來好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.49,0:07:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看我去買點飲料好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.36,0:07:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我要…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.27,0:07:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心，鳩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.27,0:08:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳不可以游得太遠，聽到沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.04,0:08:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.78,0:08:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.31,0:08:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事，習慣了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.59,0:08:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會打架還是比不過會做便當吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.59,0:08:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海邊真的很好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.70,0:08:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要再騙人了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.20,0:08:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虎太郎\N你看起來一點也不開心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.54,0:08:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有那回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.77,0:08:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.88,0:08:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虎太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.02,0:08:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虎太郎，你知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.26,0:08:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鈴原一個人拿不了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.86,0:08:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以，我過去幫她拿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.56,0:09:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虎太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.30,0:09:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼，虎太郎這個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.97,0:09:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.44,0:09:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要草莓哈密瓜加檸檬\N綜合刨冰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.81,0:09:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有賣這種的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.21,0:09:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在流行這樣吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.15,0:09:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.28,0:09:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才也有人買同樣的冰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.05,0:09:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好燙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.62,0:09:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早知道就應該穿上涼鞋才對
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.29,0:09:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.80,0:09:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.43,0:09:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王二郎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.40,0:09:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美咲，妳也喜歡吃這種\N草莓哈密瓜檸檬綜合冰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.57,0:09:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.54,0:09:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小時候我媽媽做給我吃的\N就是這種冰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.48,0:09:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.85,0:09:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼也剛好跑來海邊玩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.28,0:09:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟我哥公司的人一起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.49,0:09:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.16,0:09:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳跟他一起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.66,0:10:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虎太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.23,0:10:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夕子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.27,0:10:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萩子，妳怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.38,0:10:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事，只是有點頭暈而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.18,0:10:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳還是找一個陰涼的地方休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.55,0:10:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我記得附近有一家餐廳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.78,0:10:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.62,0:10:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王二郎他已經去幫我買刨冰了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.29,0:10:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳這個樣子怎麼吃刨冰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.42,0:10:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以幫妳吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.79,0:10:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託，重點不是這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.02,0:10:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話\N你們大家要把便當吃光光
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.26,0:10:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，我會負責解決
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.60,0:10:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乾脆把這個豬頭\N活埋在這裡算了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.40,0:10:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虎太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.40,0:10:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王二郎\N剛好也跟他哥公司的人來玩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.01,0:10:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.37,0:10:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王二郎原來你有哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.81,0:10:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是，可是不是什麼好哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.28,0:10:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行，抓不到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.75,0:11:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.55,0:11:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿一叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.22,0:11:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來囉…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.39,0:11:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美咲，怎麼妳也來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.73,0:11:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來王二郎的哥哥是阿一叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.80,0:11:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總裁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.34,0:11:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來你在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.64,0:11:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳不是鈴原美咲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.77,0:11:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的部下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.11,0:11:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.24,0:11:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳來得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.75,0:11:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們正準備要烤肉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.48,0:11:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們也來吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.92,0:11:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有便當可以吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.55,0:11:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會打擾你們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.99,0:11:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然不會
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.02,0:11:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了\N那我去叫鳩子他們也來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.39,0:11:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳說什麼，光速鈴鹿也來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.29,0:11:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.66,0:11:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虎太郎，走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.63,0:11:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.63,0:11:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等你們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.43,0:11:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.70,0:11:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身材看起來還是中學生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.77,0:11:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要懲罰你，三秒鐘吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.37,0:11:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥，反正遲早要見面的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.61,0:11:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是她還沒有做好心理準備
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.55,0:12:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是覺得萩子應該可以應付
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.98,0:12:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萩子剛才說她有點不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.92,0:12:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,修二夫妻已經先帶她\N去附近的餐廳休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.97,0:12:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到王二郎的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.77,0:12:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然會是阿一叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.01,0:12:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼上次的那場比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.11,0:12:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也等於是他們兄弟對決了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.85,0:12:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.58,0:12:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我跟美咲獲勝了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.25,0:12:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥是天使領域的創始人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.79,0:12:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弟弟是貴公子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.92,0:12:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,維札特這麼厲害\N是因為血統優良吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.23,0:12:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真要說血統的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.60,0:12:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.10,0:12:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了，大家來吃烤肉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.18,0:13:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣，好點了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.94,0:13:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舒服多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.28,0:13:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概是天氣太熱的關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.18,0:13:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三原
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.81,0:13:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們開始烤肉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.52,0:13:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡有我陪著就行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.55,0:13:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們趕快去吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.35,0:13:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.72,0:13:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.26,0:13:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.66,0:13:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我去去就回來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.50,0:13:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子也到海邊來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.67,0:13:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一想到妳們會碰面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.41,0:13:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就心驚肉跳的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.85,0:13:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.12,0:13:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們要多吃一點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.69,0:13:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們開動了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.29,0:13:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有這個\N不嫌棄的話也請嚐嚐看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.89,0:13:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我自己做的便當
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.70,0:13:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稻田先生\N請你把那個便當也打開
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.83,0:14:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.60,0:14:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菜色一模一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.97,0:14:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有章魚小香腸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.47,0:14:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有煎蛋捲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.61,0:14:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有炸雞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.58,0:14:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連魚板都一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.51,0:14:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的都一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.85,0:14:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪了，怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.15,0:14:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個便當是萩子她…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.39,0:14:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看起來好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.89,0:14:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烤肉也烤得香噴噴的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.49,0:14:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我又招誰惹誰了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.46,0:14:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來…多吃點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.17,0:14:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.07,0:14:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連味道都一模一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.87,0:14:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美咲，肉已經烤好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.94,0:14:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你，王二郎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.91,0:14:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好燙…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.65,0:14:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肉已經烤好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.45,0:14:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.95,0:14:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再走…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.85,0:14:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再往右邊一點，右邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.49,0:14:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心一點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.30,0:15:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子她玩得開心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.93,0:15:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳就在這裡看，不過去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.04,0:15:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在還不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.87,0:15:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看我先搭電車回去好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.41,0:15:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經有點累了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.66,0:15:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，各位，最後還有煙火晚會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.09,0:15:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尾形，看來你今天最賣力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.40,0:15:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對，因為公司\N只有今天才放假一天嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.17,0:15:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了可憐的尾形哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.10,0:15:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們就陪他玩一玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.81,0:15:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放煙火最好玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.81,0:15:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.94,0:15:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最好玩了，對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.48,0:15:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尾形哥哥\N你每天工作一定很可憐對不對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.72,0:15:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你被小孩子同情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.52,0:16:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底誰才是小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.95,0:16:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我們就散步到日落為止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.79,0:16:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們去那邊走一走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.30,0:16:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.06,0:16:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看我們也應該回去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.27,0:16:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果太晚回去會挨罵的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.27,0:16:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虎太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.47,0:16:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以送你們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.81,0:16:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,車子還坐得下很多人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.84,0:16:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.21,0:16:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虎太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.11,0:16:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起，就聽你們的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.55,0:16:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虎太郎就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.45,0:16:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想回去看電視\N所以才這麼緊張的對不對
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.69,0:16:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們每一次都這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.69,0:16:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.79,0:16:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.61,0:16:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩送她到車站
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.31,0:17:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.91,0:17:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛急著搭電車
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.78,0:17:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就可以吃鐵路便當了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.89,0:17:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.09,0:17:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我也要先走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.29,0:17:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們一起買便當吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.06,0:17:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走囉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.91,0:17:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.78,0:17:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直走到那頭為止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.85,0:17:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我忘記把小光一起帶出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.19,0:17:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.29,0:17:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也對
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.94,0:18:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美咲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.58,0:18:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.21,0:18:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳的名字是誰幫妳取的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.42,0:18:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個，我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.49,0:18:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳的名字很好聽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.92,0:18:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.09,0:18:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的名字也很特別
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.69,0:18:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我哥哥叫做一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.73,0:18:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿一叔叔原來叫一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.66,0:18:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過，王二郎聽起來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.17,0:18:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比一郎要神氣多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.50,0:18:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最滿意的就是這一點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.64,0:18:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們兄弟的感情不好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.04,0:18:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看起來會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.41,0:18:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兄弟可以為同樣的興趣努力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.35,0:18:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實真的讓我好羨慕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.55,0:18:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小咲咲也真是的\N她竟然連小光都忘了帶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.46,0:18:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她平常總是抓著不放的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.90,0:18:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了，虎太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.53,0:19:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,珠代，我們也去鈴原那裡找她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.93,0:19:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虎太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.54,0:19:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.94,0:19:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虎太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.07,0:19:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有沒有聽到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.88,0:19:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實我…我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.15,0:19:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.35,0:19:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你心裡一直偷偷的\N喜歡著小咲咲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.42,0:19:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.84,0:19:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.97,0:19:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我從小就一直很喜歡你\N虎太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.41,0:20:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位，我買了冷飲回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.83,0:20:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.90,0:20:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，剛才冷落了妳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.04,0:20:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虎太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.47,0:20:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看，很漂亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.75,0:20:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我們來比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.58,0:21:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看誰的仙女棒可以撐最久
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.85,0:21:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總裁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.55,0:21:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也太老土了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.16,0:21:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,煙花要放大支的才過癮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.16,0:21:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,豬頭，你以為仙女棒老土
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.09,0:21:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可見你還只是個小毛頭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.50,0:21:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒聽說仙女棒燒越久\N就表示願望能夠實現嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.40,0:21:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.84,0:21:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.34,0:21:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那只剩下我跟阿一叔叔較量了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.88,0:21:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.84,0:21:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,點火
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.55,0:22:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不禁開始習慣依賴你的溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.03,0:23:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歷經無數夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.81,0:23:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我終於發現最重要的
